{"tid":2308960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學民三子判刑︱8年戰友黃莉莉：三人押上了人生","createTime":"2020-12-02T08:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T15:01:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c72f94366a6a9def2c5e097597411f9b403858a8","tid":2308960,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:30:27.000Z","msg":"從學民思潮走到香港眾志，再到《港區國安法》實施前夕，香港眾志宣佈解散，8年間，那些年的中學生已長成大人，參與並見證着香港的風風雨雨。6.21包圍警總案今判決，黃之鋒與林朗彥已非首次入獄，而周庭則面臨首次監禁。三人的多年戰友﹑從反國民絕食一起走到今天的黃莉莉坦言，最擔心的是周庭，「好多時佢嘅軟弱都唔會表露喺人前，會令人擔心同埋在意啲」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/GNUIUYQXKNGTRAEXIBXINOWNQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FGNUIUYQXKNGTRAEXIBXINOWNQE%2F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2X4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=8e55fa03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FGNUIUYQXKNGTRAEXIBXINOWNQE%2F&h=a3ab152e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/GNUIUYQXKNGTRAEXIBXINOWNQE/</a>"},{"pid":"cf2bf0179781779da67b880a584aabc7e21e4586","tid":2308960,"uid":7369,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:34:17.000Z","msg":"睇得出周庭其實好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5d46dbe1fa784fa5aead055d477c2945344b85","tid":2308960,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cf2bf0179781779da67b880a584aabc7e21e4586","tid":2308960,"uid":7369,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:34:17.000Z","msg":"睇得出周庭其實好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:49:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39087da959529d0992d929cdcf85e1c4cf3a58a","tid":2308960,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-0